How to install helm?
https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/
https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.10.3-linux-amd64.tar.gz

Download your desired version
Unpack it (tar -zxvf helm-v3.0.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz)
(mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm)

